class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.28</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>过去曾是黑帮成员的东哲，努力洗清黑暗的过去，和天使般善良的妻子智秀过着平凡的生活某天妻子智秀遭到绑架。不久，一通陌生来电表示要付东哲一笔钱，要求东哲将妻子卖给他…东哲将用行动证明绑匪惹错了人！</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/59477/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/13642/" data-original="http://pic.iqiyi6123.com/upload/vod/2019-01-17/154771595818.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">3.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center"></span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/13642/">愤怒的小鸟</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E6%9D%B0%E6%A3%AE%C2%B7%E8%8B%8F%E6%88%B4%E5%A5%87%E6%96%AF------------/" target="_blank">杰森·苏戴奇斯</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E4%B9%94%E4%BB%80%C2%B7%E5%8A%A0%E5%BE%B7------------/" target="_blank">乔什·加德</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E4%B8%B9%E5%B0%BC%C2%B7%E9%BA%A6%E5%85%8B%E5%B8%83%E8%8E%B1%E5%BE%B7------------/" target="_blank">丹尼·麦克布莱德</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E7%8E%9B%E5%A8%85%C2%B7%E9%B2%81%E9%81%93%E5%A4%AB------------/" target="_blank">玛娅·鲁道夫</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E8%B4%B9%E6%A0%BC%E5%B0%94%C2%B7%E9%9B%B7%E5%88%A9--------/" target="_blank">费格尔·雷利</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-----%E5%85%8B%E9%9B%B7%C2%B7%E5%8D%A1%E6%8F%90%E6%96%AF--------/" target="_blank">克雷·卡提斯</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/22/" target="_blank">其他片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span>未知</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2016/" target="_blank">2016</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>在一座与世隔绝的小岛上，生活着种类繁多且快乐无忧的小鸟不过他们中间总有异类存在，比如离群索居的胖红（杰森·苏戴奇斯 Jason Sudeikis 配音），孤儿出身且有些另类的怪异容貌让他成为其他鸟儿嘲笑和奚落的对象。久而久之，胖红也养成了促狭易怒的性格。在被法官叛出参 加情绪管理课程期间，他结识了速</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/13642/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/80462/" data-original="https://img.1977zy.cc/upload/vod/2019-06-20/201906201560973194.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">3.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD1280高清中英双字版</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/80462/">愤怒的阿登</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span>未知</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span>未知</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/12/" target="_blank">战争片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD-----------/" target="_blank">美国</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2014/" target="_blank">2014</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>1944年末，纳粹党发动了一场战役，一支美国坦克部队被困在敌人后方盟军行动阿登愤怒即将开始，当坦克指挥官移动到附近的孤儿院，拯救无辜的孩子们。</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/80462/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/78981/" data-original="https://img.1977zy.cc/upload/vod/2019-05-24/201905241558627456.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">1.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD1280韩语高清</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/78981/">愤怒的画家</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span>未知</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span>未知</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/20/" target="_blank">福利</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E9%9F%A9%E5%9B%BD-----------/" target="_blank">韩国</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2018/" target="_blank">2018</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>서 감지되는 위기의 시그널을 포착하고 과감히 사표를 던진 금융맨 ‘윤정학’(유아인)은&nbsp;국가부도의 위기에 투자하는 역베팅을 결심, 투자자들을 모으기 시</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/78981/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/8095/" data-original="http://pic.iqiyi6123.com/upload/vod/2019-01-17/154771374810.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">10.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center"></span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/8095/">愤怒的公牛2</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E6%B1%A4%E5%A7%86%C2%B7%E5%A1%9E%E5%85%B9%E6%91%A9%E5%B0%94------------/" target="_blank">汤姆·塞兹摩尔</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%A8%81%E5%BB%89%C2%B7%E5%BC%97%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%AF------------/" target="_blank">威廉·弗西斯</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E4%B9%94%C2%B7%E6%9B%BC%E7%89%B9%E7%BA%B3------------/" target="_blank">乔·曼特纳</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E4%BF%9D%E7%BD%97%C2%B7%E7%B4%A2%E7%BB%B4%E8%AF%BA------------/" target="_blank">保罗·索维诺</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a hre